abstract: Zynga is pressing ahead with its initial public offering plans amid continuing market volatility, which has recently delayed or derailed several I.P.O.'s.

lead_paragraph: Zynga, the online gaming giant, is one step closer to the public markets.

headline.main: Zynga Is Headed for the Nasdaq
